        On <strong>Oct 19</strong>, we’re making it easier to schedule, prepare, and conduct interviews across the app. Whether you plan ahead with workflow helpers or do your interviews ad hoc, we’ve got you covered. Soon you’ll be able to quickly add or create interviews on a candidate profile, create custom question types, and &mdash; for Google calendar users &mdash; invite teammates to sync their calendars without logging into Jazz.
      </p>
