        </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Add an interview while on a candidate’s profile, even if it doesn’t exist in the job workflow.</li>
          <li>Create new interview templates without going to the Admin section.</li>
          <li>Build interviews with different question types, including text-based, multiple choice, and numeric entry.</li>
          <li>Add and reorder questions during the interview directly in the Interview Guide.</li>
          <li>See whether people have accepted or declined an interview invitation from the Interview tab.</li>
          <li>Reschedule and cancel interviews from the Interview tab.</li>
          <li><strong>Special Note</strong>: Customers who use Google calendar can send a link to their teammates that will allow them to sync their calendars without needing to sign into Jazz.</li>
        </ul>
